  "title": "logistic project manager",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Manage and oversee transportation projects from start to finish.</li><li>Develop and implement project plans and schedules.</li><li>Coordinate with internal and external stakeholders to ensure timely delivery and smooth operation.</li><li>Monitor project progress, budget, and performance against established goals and objectives.</li><li>Identify and mitigate project risks and issues.</li><li>Communicate regularly with clients, vendors, and team members to ensure that all parties are aligned.</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety regulations, industry standards, and company policies and procedures.</li><li>Provide regular status updates and reports to upper management.</li><li>Continuously evaluate and improve project processes and procedures to increase efficiency and effectiveness.</li></ul>",
